《'''卑鄙的我：电影原声带'''》（{{lang-en|''Despicable Me: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack''}}）是为[[卑鄙的我|同名电影]]的电影配乐，2010年7月6日发布。由法瑞尔·威廉姆斯为电影创作、演奏并制作并由{{link-en|黛丝蒂妮&帕丽斯|Destinee & Paris}}、{{link-en|The Sylvers}}、[[罗宾·西克|罗宾·西克]]、[[比吉斯|比吉斯]]和{{link-en|大卫·比斯巴尔|David Bisbal}}等演奏的新曲组成<ref name="prnewswire">{{cite news|title=DESPICABLE ME: ORIGINAL MOTION PICTURE SOUNDTRACK Album to be Released July 6 on Star Trak/Interscope|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/despicable-me-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-album-to-be-released-july-6-on-star-trakinterscope-96357559.html|accessdate=2013-08-08|newspaper=PR Newswire|date=2010-06-15|language=en|archive-date=2011-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111225081945/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/despicable-me-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-album-to-be-released-july-6-on-star-trakinterscope-96357559.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

电影配乐由法瑞尔·威廉姆斯和{{link-en|黑特·佩雷拉|Heitor Pereira}}合作谱写，并由[[汉斯·季默|汉斯·季默]]负责出品。由{{link-en|好莱坞工作室交响乐团|Hollywood Studio Symphony}}{{refnest|group="注释"|译名参考自新浪网<ref name="sina">{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2009-02-09/17022368676.shtml|title=《龙珠》鼓乐飞扬 主创赴录音棚探班照公开(图)|date=2009-02-09|publisher=新浪娱乐|accessdate=2014-01-17|author=心之洛|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304135955/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2009-02-09/17022368676.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}在[[二十世纪福克斯|二十世纪福克斯]]的{{link-en|纽曼配乐舞台|Newman Scoring Stage}}{{refnest|group="注释"|译名参考自新浪网<ref name="sina"/>}}以67人合奏录制<ref>{{cite news |last=Goldwasser |first=Dan |url=http://www.scoringsessions.com/news/219 |title=Heitor Pereira scores 'Despicable Me' |work=ScoringSessions.com |date=2010-06-30 |accessdate=2010-06-30 |language=en |archive-date=2010-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100927231616/http://scoringsessions.com/news/219/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年11月配乐集中的8支曲子出现在网站MagicBoxMusic.com上，而此时电影的配乐集尚未正式发售<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.magicboxmusic.com/virtualresume/details.php?id=DM|title="Despicable Me"|publisher=MagicBoxMusic.com|accessdate=2011-04-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322081539/http://www.magicboxmusic.com/virtualresume/details.php?id=DM|archivedate=2012-03-22|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://theneptunes.org/despicable-me-promo-score-2010 |title='Despicable Me' Promo Score (2010) |author=Mika |work=TheNeptunes.org |date=2010-11-10 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |language=en |archive-date=2010-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101215120358/http://theneptunes.org/despicable-me-promo-score-2010/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

影片中出现的两首歌曲《Despicable Me》和《Prettiest Girls》也出现在了[[第83届奥斯卡金像奖|第83届奥斯卡奖]]的最佳原创歌曲入围名单中。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/12/oscar-taps-41-movie-tunes-for-original-song-category/ |title=Oscar Taps 41 Movie Tunes For Original Song Category |work=Deadline Hollywood |date=2010-12-15 |accessdate=2012-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004213014/http://www.deadline.com/2010/12/oscar-taps-41-movie-tunes-for-original-song-category/ |archivedate=2013-10-04 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

